                        <p>College: The Academic Foundation</p>
                        <p>For those seeking a formal degree, colleges offer programs in UI/UX design, such as degrees in Human-Computer Interaction or Interaction Design. This traditional academic path provides a comprehensive education but comes with its own set of limitations like long duration, heavy on pocket, etc.</p>
